name: Anesvarrett Dragon
desc: When a Link Monster's effect is activated that targets this card (Quick Effect): You can destroy this card, then make 1 face-up monster on the field unable to attack, also it has its effects negated. During the End Phase, if this card is in the GY because it was destroyed by battle or card effect and sent there from the field this turn: You can Special Summon 1 "varrett" monster from your Deck, except "Anesvarrett Dragon". You can only use each effect of "Anesvarrett Dragon" once per turn.
